evals.prompt:
Our Cucumber + Playwright e2e suite has step definitions like this:

When('the user completes checkout', async () => {
  await page.click('#cart-icon');
  await page.fill('#card-number', '4242424242424242');
  await page.fill('#cvv', '123');
  await page.click('[data-test="submit-payment"]');
  await page.waitForSelector('.confirmation');
});

We have about 60 of these and every time the frontend team renames a class we spend a day fixing them. What should we be doing differently?
